                            <section id="alt-services" class="alt-services">
                <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
                    <div class="row justify-content-around gy-4">
                                                <div class="col-lg-5 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
                                                            <h2>Seamont Autograph Collection Residence</h2>
                                                                                        <p class="text-justify"> <p>Seamont Autograph Collection Residences on Shams Al Reem Island embody the art of living where the sea meets the sky. Developed by Royal Development Holding and SAAS Properties, this visionary project features two sculpted towers offering 1 to 4-bedroom apartments, duplexes, and penthouses with breathtaking Arabian Gulf views. Seamont blends Marriott&rsquo;s signature hospitality with refined coastal design, providing residents exclusive Bonvoy privileges, resort-style amenities, and a serene waterfront lifestyle surrounded by Abu Dhabi&rsquo;s most dynamic cultural and leisure destinations.</p></p>
                                                    </div>
                        
                                                 <div class="col-lg-6 has-bg">
                            <div class="before">
