                <!--- Description2 -->
        <section class="pb-0">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="text-justify"><strong></strong></h2>
                <p class="text-justify"> <h1>Seamont Autograph Collection Residences &ndash; Where the Sea Meets the Sky</h1>
<p data-start="512" data-end="1082">Set on the tranquil shores of Shams, Reem Island, Seamont Autograph Collection Residences redefines luxury coastal living in Abu Dhabi. A visionary collaboration between Royal Development Holding and SAAS Properties, this exclusive waterfront development reflects the grace of nautical design and the prestige of Marriott International&rsquo;s Autograph Collection. Seamont is a sanctuary where the beauty of the sea meets the serenity of the sky, offering a life of calm, sophistication, and seamless connection to the city&rsquo;s cultural and business hubs.</p>
<h3 data-start="1089" data-end="1121">Key Project Highlights</h3>
<ul>
<li data-start="1124" data-end="1169">Location: Shams, Reem Island, Abu Dhabi</li>
<li data-start="1172" data-end="1232">Developer: Royal Development Holding &amp; SAAS Properties</li>
<li data-start="1235" data-end="1289">Brand Partnership: Marriott Autograph Collection</li>
<li data-start="1292" data-end="1325">Total Units: 497 residences</li>
<li data-start="1328" data-end="1388">Configuration: 1 to 3 Bedroom Simplex, 3 or 4 Bedroom Duplex</li>
<li data-start="1391" data-end="1433">Sizes: From 731 sq.ft to 6,233 sq.ft</li>
<li data-start="1436" data-end="1486">Building Height: G + 22 Floors (Twin Towers)</li>
<li data-start="1489" data-end="1544">Views: Panoramic Arabian Gulf &amp; Abu Dhabi Skyline</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="1551" data-end="1577">Property Details</h3>
<p data-start="1578" data-end="2049">Seamont Autograph Collection comprises two sculpted high-rise towers rising gracefully above a shared podium, featuring 497 impeccably designed homes. The collection includes elegant 1 to 3 bedroom simplex apartments and 3&ndash;4 bedroom duplex residences, each designed to capture uninterrupted sea views and skyline panoramas. Expansive balconies, private terrace gardens, and open layouts connect residents directly with the natural rhythm of the waterfront.&nbsp;Ground-level townhouses offer private gardens, while upper-level penthouses provide exclusive duplex layouts for an elevated sense of privacy and grandeur. Every home reflects refined craftsmanship, modern comfort, and an atmosphere of coastal tranquility.</p>
<h3 data-start="2316" data-end="2347">Lifestyle &amp; Amenities</h3>
<p data-start="2348" data-end="2553">Seamont introduces a lifestyle inspired by Marriott&rsquo;s signature hospitality, offering both exclusivity and comfort. Residents enjoy access to a curated range of resort-style amenities, including:</p>
<ul>
<li data-start="2556" data-end="2600">Infinity swimming pool overlooking the sea</li>
<li data-start="2603" data-end="2645">Fully equipped gymnasium and yoga studio</li>
<li data-start="2648" data-end="2687">Steam room, sauna, and wellness areas</li>
<li data-start="2690" data-end="2734">Indoor &amp; outdoor kids&rsquo; play zones and pool</li>
<li data-start="2737" data-end="2782">Padel tennis court and outdoor fitness area</li>
<li data-start="2785" data-end="2836">Private cinema, games room, and residents&rsquo; lounge</li>
<li data-start="2839" data-end="2888">Business lounge and boardroom for professionals</li>
<li data-start="2891" data-end="2944">Concierge service, valet parking, and 24/7 security</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2946" data-end="3171">Adding to its distinction, homeowners receive Marriott Bonvoy Gold Elite Membership, unlocking personalized services, global privileges, and a hospitality standard that transforms daily life into a five-star experience.</p>
<h3 data-start="3178" data-end="3212">Architecture &amp; Interiors</h3>
<p data-start="3213" data-end="3674">Inspired by the rhythms of the sea, Seamont&rsquo;s architecture flows with elegant curvature and organic form. The twin towers rise from a shared podium connected to the waterfront promenade, blending modern minimalism with maritime heritage. Inside, floor-to-ceiling windows, soft neutral palettes, and premium finishes evoke a calm, light-filled aesthetic. Every residence is a masterpiece of balance &mdash; where design meets nature, and form meets function.</p>
<h3 data-start="3681" data-end="3714">Location &amp; Connectivity</h3>
<p data-start="3715" data-end="4101">Perfectly positioned on Reem Island, Seamont offers both seclusion and accessibility. The development is just 5 minutes from Maryah Island, 7 minutes from Louvre Abu Dhabi, and 25 minutes from Abu Dhabi International Airport. Residents enjoy easy access to retail, dining, healthcare, and educational destinations while remaining surrounded by the calm of the sea.</p>
<p data-start="4131" data-end="4500">Seamont Autograph Collection Residences embody the harmony of sea and sky &mdash; a refined statement of luxury, design, and lifestyle. Combining the elegance of Marriott&rsquo;s Autograph Collection with the tranquility of Reem Island&rsquo;s waterfront, Seamont is more than a home &mdash; it&rsquo;s a timeless expression of balance, beauty, and belonging in the heart of Abu Dhabi.</p> </p>
            </div>
        </section>
                <!--- Description2 Ends here-->

