                    <section id="faq">
                <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
                                        <div>
                                                    <h2 class="text-dark  text-center mb-4">FAQs</h2>
                                                                    </div>
                                                            <div class="row " data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                        <div class="col-lg-1"></div>
                        <div class="col-lg-9">
                            <ul class="faq-list">
                                                                                                            <li>
                                            <div data-bs-toggle="collapse" class="collapsed question" data-bs-target="#faq21" href="#faq21">
                                                Where is Seamont Autograph Collection Residences located?
                                                <i class="fa fa-plus icon-show me-auto"></i>
                                                <i class="me-auto fa fa-close icon-close"></i>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="faq21" class="collapse" data-bs-parent=".faq-list">
                                                <p><p>It is located in the Shams district on Reem Island, Abu Dhabi, with prime waterfront positioning, promenade access, and minutes from Maryah Island and Downtown Abu Dhabi.</p></p>
                                            </div>
                                      </li>
                                                                                                                                                <li>
                                            <div data-bs-toggle="collapse" class="collapsed question" data-bs-target="#faq22" href="#faq22">
                                                What types of units are available?
                                                <i class="fa fa-plus icon-show me-auto"></i>
                                                <i class="me-auto fa fa-close icon-close"></i>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="faq22" class="collapse" data-bs-parent=".faq-list">
                                                <p><p>Seamont Autograph Collection Residences offers 497 luxury units, including 1 to 3 bedroom simplex apartments, 3 or 4 bedroom duplexes, and premium penthouses, all with sea views and high-end finishes.</p></p>
                                            </div>
                                      </li>
                                                                                                                                                <li>
                                            <div data-bs-toggle="collapse" class="collapsed question" data-bs-target="#faq23" href="#faq23">
                                                What amenities are offered?
                                                <i class="fa fa-plus icon-show me-auto"></i>
                                                <i class="me-auto fa fa-close icon-close"></i>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="faq23" class="collapse" data-bs-parent=".faq-list">
                                                <p><p>Residents enjoy waterfront infinity pools, rooftop gardens, gyms, children&rsquo;s play areas, concierge services, and covered parking.</p></p>
                                            </div>
                                      </li>
                                                                                                                                                <li>
                                            <div data-bs-toggle="collapse" class="collapsed question" data-bs-target="#faq24" href="#faq24">
                                                Are there shopping and dining options nearby?
                                                <i class="fa fa-plus icon-show me-auto"></i>
                                                <i class="me-auto fa fa-close icon-close"></i>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="faq24" class="collapse" data-bs-parent=".faq-list">
                                                <p><p>Yes. Nearby destinations include Shams Boutik Mall, Reem Mall, and Al Maryah Island&rsquo;s Galleria Mall, along with various restaurants and leisure spots.</p></p>
                                            </div>
                                      </li>
                                                                                                                                                <li>
                                            <div data-bs-toggle="collapse" class="collapsed question" data-bs-target="#faq25" href="#faq25">
                                                Who is the developer of Seamont autograph Collection Residences?
                                                <i class="fa fa-plus icon-show me-auto"></i>
                                                <i class="me-auto fa fa-close icon-close"></i>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="faq25" class="collapse" data-bs-parent=".faq-list">
                                                <p><p>The project is developed by Royal Development Holding and SAAS Properties in collaboration with Marriott International, marking Abu Dhabi&rsquo;s first Autograph Collection branded residences.</p></p>
                                            </div>
                                      </li>
                                                                                                                                                <li>
                                            <div data-bs-toggle="collapse" class="collapsed question" data-bs-target="#faq26" href="#faq26">
                                                Is it family-friendly?
                                                <i class="fa fa-plus icon-show me-auto"></i>
                                                <i class="me-auto fa fa-close icon-close"></i>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="faq26" class="collapse" data-bs-parent=".faq-list">
                                                <p><p>Yes. Reem Island hosts top schools, parks, and a multicultural community, making it ideal for families.</p></p>
                                            </div>
                                      </li>
                                                                                                                                                <li>
                                            <div data-bs-toggle="collapse" class="collapsed question" data-bs-target="#faq27" href="#faq27">
                                                What are the views from Seamont Autograph Collection Residences?
                                                <i class="fa fa-plus icon-show me-auto"></i>
                                                <i class="me-auto fa fa-close icon-close"></i>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="faq27" class="collapse" data-bs-parent=".faq-list">
                                                <p><p>Residents enjoy panoramic views of the Arabian Gulf, the Reem Island waterfront, and Abu Dhabi&rsquo;s skyline from private terraces and floor-to-ceiling windows.</p></p>
                                            </div>
                                      </li>
                                                                                                                                                <li>
                                            <div data-bs-toggle="collapse" class="collapsed question" data-bs-target="#faq28" href="#faq28">
                                                What makes Seamont Autograph Collection Residences unique?
                                                <i class="fa fa-plus icon-show me-auto"></i>
                                                <i class="me-auto fa fa-close icon-close"></i>
                                            </div>
                                            <div id="faq28" class="collapse" data-bs-parent=".faq-list">
                                                <p><p>As Abu Dhabi&rsquo;s first Autograph Collection branded residences, it combines luxury living with Marriott-level hospitality, premium amenities, and a prime waterfront location on Reem Island.</p></p>
                                            </div>
                                      </li>
                                                                                                </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                                        </div>
            </section>
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        
        

